---
description: Retrieval subsystem
globs: ["src/biolit/retrieval/**", "src/biolit/ingest/**"]
alwaysApply: false
---
- Pipeline: esearch -> efetch/esummary -> BM25 + MedCPT dense -> RRF fuse -> MedCPT cross-encoder rerank.
- Always send NCBI tool+email+api_key params. Back off on 429. Cache E-utilities responses in Redis.
- Return per-retriever scores and highlighted spans. Persist queries and hits.
- MedCPT models: ncbi/MedCPT-Query-Encoder, -Article-Encoder, -Cross-Encoder. Load once, reuse.
